Virtual Building Empire - Additional Terms

1. GAME ASSETS AND CONTENT
   - All game assets, including but not limited to character designs, building
     layouts, and LUNC token mechanics, are proprietary to Virtual Building Empire.
   - Users are granted a license to use these assets solely within the context
     of the Virtual Building Empire game.

2. SMART CONTRACTS
   - The smart contracts included in this repository are provided for educational
     and development purposes.
   - Deployment and use of these contracts in production environments should only
     be done after proper security auditing.
   - The authors assume no responsibility for financial losses resulting from
     smart contract vulnerabilities or exploits.

3. BLOCKCHAIN INTERACTIONS
   - Users interact with blockchain networks at their own risk.
   - Gas fees, transaction costs, and network congestion are outside the control
     of the Virtual Building Empire developers.
   - Always verify contract addresses and transaction details before confirming
     any blockchain transactions.

4. VIRTUAL CURRENCY (LUNC)
   - LUNC tokens are virtual game currency with no real-world monetary value.
   - LUNC tokens are not securities, investments, or financial instruments.
   - The game is designed for entertainment purposes only.

5. NFT CHARACTER OWNERSHIP
   - NFT characters represent digital collectibles within the game ecosystem.
   - Character ownership is subject to the terms of the underlying blockchain
     network and smart contract functionality.
   - Characters have no inherent value outside the Virtual Building Empire game.

6. MARKETPLACE TRANSACTIONS
   - All marketplace transactions are conducted between users.
   - Virtual Building Empire facilitates but does not guarantee marketplace
     transactions.
   - Users are responsible for their own due diligence when trading characters.

7. GAME MECHANICS AND BALANCE
   - Game mechanics, earning rates, and character attributes may be updated to
     maintain game balance and user experience.
   - Such updates will be communicated through official channels.
   - No guarantees are made regarding future earning potential or character values.

8. COMMUNITY GUIDELINES
   - Users must comply with community guidelines and terms of service.
   - Cheating, exploiting, or attempting to manipulate game mechanics is prohibited.
   - Users found violating guidelines may have their access restricted.

9. INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY
   - The Virtual Building Empire brand, logos, and original creative content are
